{d}nin-ŋeš-zid-da diŋir gu₃-de₂-a ensi₂ lagaš{ki}\gen lu₂ e₂-an-na\abs in-du₃-a-kam {d}inana nin kur-kur-ra nin-a-ni\dat gu₃-de₂-a mu gil-sa\gen ensi₂ lagaš{ki}\gen lu₂ e₂-ninnu {d}nin-ŋir₂-su-ka\abs in-du₃-a\erg ud {d}inana-ke₄ igi nam-til₃-ka-ni\abs mu-ši-bar-ra-a gu₃-de₂-a ensi₂ lagaš{ki}\gen ŋeštug₂ daŋal-a-kam arad₂ nin-a-ni\dat ki\abs aŋ₂-am₃ bisaŋ u₃-šub-ba-ka
5al2 ŋeš\abs ba-hur ka-al-ka\l2 urin\abs ba-mul im-bi\abs ki dadag-ga-a
5al2 im-mi-lu šeg₁₂-bi\abs ki sikil-a
